      protected JQLAST Optimizer.deMorgan(JQLAST tree)
      Implements DeMorgans rule:
      NOT (a AND b) -> NOT a OR NOT b
      NOT (a OR b) -> NOT a AND NOT b
      NOT (NOT a) -> a
      The method assumes that the tree passed as an argument does not include the initial NOT.
